57#include "smb_kernelops.h"
58
59int
60smb_read(struct smb_ctx *ctx, smbfh fh, off_t offset, size_t count, char *dst)
61{
62 struct smbioc_rw rwrq;
63
64 rwrq.ioc_fh = fh;
65 rwrq.ioc_base = dst;
66 rwrq.ioc_cnt = count;
67 rwrq.ioc_offset = offset;
68 if (smb_kops.ko_ioctl(ctx->ct_fd, SMBIOC_READ, &rwrq) == -1)
69 return -1;
70 return rwrq.ioc_cnt;
71}
72
73int
74smb_write(struct smb_ctx *ctx, smbfh fh, off_t offset, size_t count,
75 const char *src)
76{
77 struct smbioc_rw rwrq;
78
79 rwrq.ioc_fh = fh;
80 rwrq.ioc_base = __UNCONST(src);
81 rwrq.ioc_cnt = count;
82 rwrq.ioc_offset = offset;
83 if (smb_kops.ko_ioctl(ctx->ct_fd, SMBIOC_WRITE, &rwrq) == -1)
84 return -1;
85 return rwrq.ioc_cnt;
86}
